 "张凌赫", "b": "축옥", "w": 1}, {"a": "무안후", "b": "장릉혁", "w": 1}, {"a": "무안후", "b": "축옥", "w": 1}, {"a": "장릉혁", "b": "축옥", "w": 1}, {"a": "dubai", "b": "oil", "w": 1}, {"a": "oil", "b": "usoil", "w": 1}, {"a": "oil", "b": "supply", "w": 1}, {"a": "energy", "b": "oil", "w": 1}, {"a": "oil", "b": "theofficials", "w": 1}, {"a": "oil", "b": "wti", "w": 1}]}, "top_tweets": [{"id": "2066344980403179857", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2066344980403179857", "text": "Trump says the deal is complete, and now it’s time for the 500 some vessels trapped in the Gulf since the start of the war to exit. #OOTT https://t.co/aNBgDPbgKC", "time": "02:20", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 17704, "likes": 113, "replies": 17, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2066347414135476367", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2066347414135476367", "text": "And then let’s not forget how fragile the situation is…Netanyahu just told Trump Israeli forces will NOT withdraw from Lebanon, and Israel does NOT consider itself bound by the Lebanon clause in the US-Iran MoU. Directly rejecting of a core pillar of the deal. #OOTT", "time": "02:29", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 5561, "likes": 38, "replies": 9, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2066348854107087123", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2066348854107087123", "text": "The expected drop in oil prices on the headlines is happening, but this war did cause damage that’s not being reflected yet in the price. One thing that took the market by surprise is the impact of price manipulation. #OOTT https://t.co/qUQBWbPYrN", "time": "02:35", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 47007, "likes": 411, "replies": 34, "retweets": 35, "quotes": 4, "bookmarks": 14, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2066352680566448605", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2066352680566448605", "text": "Now that the “deal is done”… who will be left to mop up the mess and damage caused by the conflict? #OOTT", "time": "02:50", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 14059, "likes": 100, "replies": 12, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2066364912440422833", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2066364912440422833", "text": "We are celebrating status quo (IF it even happens) @ianbremmer #OOTT", "time": "03:39", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 21672, "likes": 120, "replies": 9, "retweets": 13, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 6, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2066368590928810057", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2066368590928810057", "text": "Strait of Hormuz oil backlog could take weeks to clear after US-Iran deal\nPrices slip even as analysts warn flows may be slow to recover and remain vulnerable to renewed disruption #oott \nhttps://t.co/YVjaKgV5iF", "time": "03:53", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 7565, "likes": 82, "replies": 8, "retweets": 18, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 11, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2066373672961515786", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2066373672961515786", "text": "Oil Executives Are Sounding the Alarm Over Dwindling Stockpiles\nEven if the Strait of Hormuz soon reopens, it would likely take months for the U.S. to replenish its depleted oil inventories, keeping prices elevated #oott https://t.co/W5p0stNUIe", "time": "04:14", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 10835, "likes": 83, "replies": 6, "retweets": 23, "quotes": 5, "bookmarks": 12, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2066403099523051950", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2066403099523051950", "text": "Brent futures curve in USD/bbl (today, one week ago and one month ago) #OOTT https://t.co/wTPXoFFCTt", "time": "06:11", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 13622, "likes": 34, "replies": 0, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 7, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2066404221423911343", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2066404221423911343", "text": "Last week (June 8), before the US-Iran deal was announced, I published this @Opinion column about the re-start of oil production in the Persian Gulf region. \n\nI argued it would go much faster than many are expecting. I still think that's the case.\n\n https://t.co/oav02e1Rdk", "time": "06:15", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 58146, "likes": 335, "replies": 24, "retweets": 75, "quotes": 11, "bookmarks": 57, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2066413339320914386", "url": "https://x.com/JuneGoh_Sparta/status/2066413339320914386", "text": "Let's see how this plays out.\n\n#oott", "time": "06:51", "author": "JuneGoh_Sparta", "author_name": "June Goh", "followers": 18022, "views": 9995, "likes": 77, "replies": 6, "retweets": 18, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 20, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2066437708558295271", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2066437708558295271", "text": "3..., 2..., 1... \n\nThe oil bulls about to switch from \"tank bottoms!!!” to \"every day WTI is above $80 is a great day\"", "time": "08:28", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 197403, "likes": 656, "replies": 112, "retweets": 52, "quotes": 16, "bookmarks": 52, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2066476247824130215", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2066476247824130215", "text": "What a remarkable outcome: the world's largest ever oil supply disruption failed to create a major energy crisis.\n\nThe IEA said 2026 shock was worst than 1973, 1979 and 2022 together. And yet, the cost of oil, natural gas, electricity and coal never surpassed the previous peaks.", "time": "11:01", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 967391, "likes": 5252, "replies": 373, "retweets": 823, "quotes": 166, "bookmarks": 658, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Supply outlook", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2066510514025328651", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2066510514025328651", "text": "President Trump on social media: \n\n\"Ships are starting to move, many loaded up with Oil, out of the Strait of Hormuz. They are going along the Southern “Highway,” which is totally safe, secure, and pristine. There are other areas of travel, also!!! President DJT\"", "time": "13:17", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 31352, "likes": 167, "replies": 26, "retweets": 22, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 13, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2066569785584877874", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2066569785584877874", "text": "US SPR crude inventories fell by ~8.9mb w/w to a multi year low of 340.3mb last week #oott     \nSour down ~4.1mb to 211.9mb   \nSweet down ~4.9mb to 128.3mb https://t.co/gQJCu8FIG4", "time": "17:13", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 84175, "likes": 192, "replies": 14, "retweets": 32, "quotes": 6, "bookmarks": 19, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2066598768405827856", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2066598768405827856", "text": "Despite the US-Iran deal, the SPR releases will continue for a while. Last week, DoE put ~8.89 million barrels into the market (~1.3m b/d), continuing with several weeks of &gt;1m b/d releases that are helping to keep the American oil market better supplied.", "time": "19:08", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 52158, "likes": 302, "replies": 34, "retweets": 42, "quotes": 9, "bookmarks": 29, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2066657089770987743", "url": "https://x.com/OilandEnergy/status/2066657089770987743", "text": "Venezuela’s oil comeback is accelerating. Exports hit a 7-year high of 1.25 million bpd in May, up 61% from a year ago, as the U.S. eases operating restrictions and international firms return. Output could reach 1.5 million bpd by 2027. #OilMarkets #Venezuela #OOTT \n\nhttps://t.co/jj8BQK0q7u", "time": "23:00", "author": "OilandEnergy", "author_name": "OilPrice.com", "followers": 96445, "views": 9516, "likes": 51, "replies": 5, "retweets": 14, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Venezuela", "Supply outlook"]}}], "top_authors_by_tweets": [{"username": "staunovo", "name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "tweets": 26, "views": 187148, "likes": 668}, {"username": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11920, "tweets": 18, "views": 34523, "likes": 157}, {"username": "Amena__Bakr", "name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "tweets": 8, "views": 127519, "likes": 885}, {"username": "JavierBlas", "name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "tweets": 5, "views": 1306450, "likes": 6712}, {"username": "Energy_Tidbits", "name": "Dan Tsubouchi", "followers": 15856, "tweets": 3, "views": 6562, "likes": 11}], "top_authors_by_views": [{"username": "JavierBlas", "name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "tweets": 5, "views": 1306450, "likes": 6712}, {"username": "staunovo", "name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "tweets": 26, "views": 187148, "likes": 668}, {"username": "Amena__Bakr", "name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "tweets": 8, "views": 127519, "likes": 885}, {"username": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11920, "tweets": 18, "views": 34523, "likes": 157}, {"username": "LiveSquawk", "name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436347, "tweets": 3, "views": 20265, "likes": 29}], "sentiment": {"price": {"labeled": 111, "relevant": 110, "pos": 35, "neg": 40, "neu": 35, "index": -4.5, "index_weighted": -9.1, "opinion_share": 68.2, "hourly": [{"hour": 0, "pos": 0, "neg": 3, "neu": 3}, {"hour": 1, "pos": 0, "neg": 1, "neu": 0}, {"hour": 2, "pos": 4, "neg": 0, "neu": 3}, {"hour": 3, "pos": 2, "neg": 1, "neu": 0}, {"hour": 4, "pos": 2, "neg": 0, "neu": 2}, {"hour": 5, "pos": 0, "neg": 1, "neu": 0}, {"hour": 6, "pos": 2, "neg": 3, "neu": 1}, {"hour": 7, "pos": 1, "neg": 3, "neu": 1}, {"hour": 8, "pos": 0, "neg": 2, "neu": 1}, {"hour": 9, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 1}, {"hour": 10, "pos": 0, "neg": 3, "neu": 1}, {"hour": 11, "pos": 3, "neg": 1, "neu": 3}, {"hour": 12, "pos": 0, "neg": 1, "neu": 4}, {"hour": 13, "pos": 2, "neg": 2, "neu": 2}, {"hour": 14, "pos": 1, "neg": 0, "neu": 3}, {"hour": 15, "pos": 7, "neg": 9, "neu": 1}, {"hour": 16, "pos": 1, "neg": 1, "neu": 1}, {"hour": 17, "pos": 2, "neg": 0, "neu": 1}, {"hour": 18, "pos": 5, "neg": 2, "neu": 2}, {"hour": 19, "pos": 1, "neg": 3, "neu": 3}, {"hour": 20, "pos": 1, "neg": 1, "neu": 1}, {"hour": 21, "pos": 1, "neg": 2, "neu": 1}, {"hour": 22, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 0}, {"hour": 23, "pos": 0, "neg": 1, "neu": 0}]}, "emotional": {"labeled": 111, "relevant": 110, "pos": 4, "neg": 14, "neu": 92, "index": -9.1, "index_weighted": -11.9, "opinion_share": 16.4, "hourly": [{"hour": 0, "pos": 0, "neg": 1, "neu": 5}, {"hour": 1, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 1}, {"hour": 2, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 7}, {"hour": 3, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 3}, {"hour": 4, "pos": 0, "neg": 1, "neu": 3}, {"hour": 5, "pos": 1, "neg": 0, "neu": 0}, {"hour": 6, "pos": 0, "neg": 1, "neu": 5}, {"hour": 7, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 5}, {"hour": 8, "pos": 0, "neg": 1, "neu": 2}, {"hour": 9, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 1}, {"hour": 10, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 4}, {"hour": 11, "pos": 0, "neg": 1, "neu": 6}, {"hour": 12, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 5}, {"hour": 13, "pos": 1, "neg": 1, "neu": 4}, {"hour": 14, "pos": 1, "neg": 0, "neu": 3}, {"hour": 15, "pos": 1, "neg": 4, "neu": 12}, {"hour": 16, "pos": 0, "neg": 1, "neu": 2}, {"hour": 17, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 3}, {"hour": 18, "pos": 0, "neg": 1, "neu": 8}, {"hour": 19, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 7}, {"hour": 20, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 3}, {"hour": 21, "pos": 0, "neg": 2, "neu": 2}, {"hour": 22, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 0}, {"hour": 23, "pos": 0, "neg": 0, "neu": 1}]}}, "topics": [{"topic": "Iran", "tweets": 47, "bullish": 18, "bearish": 17, "neutral": 12}, {"topic": "Prices/technicals", "tweets": 32, "bullish": 3, "bearish": 18, "neutral": 11}, {"topic": "Geopolitics", "tweets": 31, "bullish": 8, "bearish": 11, "neutral": 12}, {"topic": "Tankers/shipping", "tweets": 22, "bullish": 14, "bearish": 3, "neutral": 5}, {"topic": "Supply outlook", "tweets": 16, "bullish": 6, "bearish": 5, "neutral": 5}, {"topic": "US inventories", "tweets": 9, "bullish": 7, "bearish": 2, "neutral": 0}, {"topic": "Demand outlook", "tweets": 8, "bullish": 3, "bearish": 4, "neutral": 1}, {"topic": "Shale/US production", "tweets": 6, "bullish": 0, "bearish": 1, "neutral": 5}, {"topic": "Refining/products", "tweets": 5, "bullish": 2, "bearish": 1, "neutral": 2}, {"topic": "OPEC+", "tweets": 2, "bullish": 1, "bearish": 1, "neutral": 0}, {"topic": "Natural gas", "tweets": 1, "bullish": 0, "bearish": 0, "neutral": 1}, {"topic": "China demand", "tweets": 1, "bullish": 1, "bearish": 0, "neutral": 0}], "summary": {"date": "2026-06-15", "overview_en": "Monday centered on the signed US-Iran MoU and Hormuz reopening pledges, depleted SPR stocks, and the takeaway that the historic supply shock never produced a full energy crisis. Price sentiment was mixed as deal-driven selling met tight-stock and deal-fragility concern; emotional tone stayed mostly neutral amid euphoria and doubt.", "overview_ru": "В понедельник в центре были подписанный MoU США–Иран и обещания открыть Ормуз, истощённые запасы SPR и вывод, что исторический шок предложения так и не перерос в полномасштабный энергетический кризис. Сентимент по цене был смешанным: продажи на сделке сталкивались с тревогой по запасам и хрупкости договорённостей; эмоциональный тон оставался в основном нейтральным на фоне эйфории и сомнений.", "themes": [{"title_en": "Historic shock, no energy crisis", "title_ru": "Исторический шок без энергокризиса", "blurb_en": "The week's most-viewed post argued the 2026 supply shock — worse than 1973, 1979 and 2022 combined per the IEA — still failed to push fuels past prior peaks.", "blurb_ru": "Самый просматриваемый пост недели утверждал, что шок предложения 2026 года — по оценке МЭА хуже, чем 1973, 1979 и 2022 вместе взятые — всё равно не вывел энергоносители выше прошлых пиков.", "text_en": "Javier Blas framed the episode as remarkable: the largest oil supply disruption on record, which the IEA called worse than the 1973, 1979 and 2022 shocks combined, did not create a major energy crisis. Oil, gas, power and coal never surpassed previous peaks, undercutting panic framing even as Hormuz diplomacy dominated the tape.", "text_ru": "Javier Blas назвал исход замечательным: крупнейший зафиксированный срыв нефтяного предложения, который МЭА оценило как хуже шоков 1973, 1979 и 2022 вместе, не породил крупного энергокризиса. Нефть, газ, электричество и уголь не превысили прошлых пиков — это ослабляло паническую рамку даже на фоне дипломатии по Ормузу.", "tone": "neutral", "tweet_ids": ["2066476247824130215"]}, {"title_en": "SPR draw to multi-year low", "title_ru": "Отбор SPR до многолетнего минимума", "blurb_en": "US SPR crude fell about 8.9 mb w/w to 340.3 mb — the lowest since 1983 and a clear bullish stock signal.", "blurb_ru": "Запасы нефти в SPR США снизились примерно на 8,9 млн барр. за неделю до 340,3 млн — минимум с 1983 года и явный бычий сигнал по запасам.", "text_en": "Staunovo flagged SPR crude down roughly 8.9 mb w/w to a multi-year low of 340.3 mb, with sour at 211.9 mb and sweet at 128.3 mb. Separately, about 75 mb of a 132 mb SPR allocation had already been released, with bids for another 40 mb exchange ending the same day.", "text_ru": "Staunovo отметил снижение нефти в SPR примерно на 8,9 млн барр. за неделю до многолетнего минимума 340,3 млн, с кислой на 211,9 млн и сладкой на 128,3 млн. Отдельно сообщалось, что из выделенных 132 млн барр. SPR уже выпущено около 75 млн, а заявки на ещё 40 млн по обмену закрывались в тот же день.", "tone": "bullish", "tweet_ids": ["2066569785584877874", "2066601507194024180"]}, {"title_en": "US-Iran MoU signed", "title_ru": "Подписан MoU США–Иран", "blurb_en": "A senior US official confirmed the MoU was signed, promising immediate Hormuz opening, blockade lift, and a possible $300 billion reconstruction fund.", "blurb_ru": "Старший чиновник США подтвердил подписание MoU с обещанием немедленного открытия Ормуза, снятия блокады и возможного фонда восстановления на $300 млрд.", "text_en": "LiveSquawk reported the US signed an MoU with Iran, with Trump and Vance among signatories. Officials said details would follow in 24–48 hours, with technical talks later in the week and frozen funds plus sanctions relief tied to Iranian performance; a possible $300 billion rebuilding fund was also cited.", "text_ru": "LiveSquawk сообщил, что США подписали MoU с Ираном, среди подписантов — Трамп и Вэнс. Чиновники обещали детали через 24–48 часов, технические переговоры на неделе и привязку разморозки средств и санкционных послаблений к выполнению обязательств Ираном; также упоминался возможный фонд восстановления на $300 млрд.", "tone": "bearish", "tweet_ids": ["2066546606854295655", "2066548400909127906"]}, {"title_en": "Selloff vs unfinished war damage", "title_ru": "Распродажа vs незакрытый ущерб войны", "blurb_en": "Headline-driven price drops were called premature by posts stressing real war damage, trapped vessels, and only a fragile return to status quo.", "blurb_ru": "Падение цены на заголовках называли преждевременным: посты подчеркивали реальный ущерб войны, застрявшие суда и лишь хрупкий возврат к status quo.", "text_en": "Amena Bakr argued the expected headline drop was underway but war damage was not yet in the price, while celebrating status quo — if it even happens. Separate notes counted some 500 vessels trapped in the Gulf and warned a Hormuz backlog could take weeks to clear even after the deal.", "text_ru": "Amena Bakr писала, что ожидаемое падение на заголовках уже идёт, но ущерб войны ещё не в цене, а «празднование status quo» уместно лишь если он вообще случится. Отдельно считали порядка 500 судов, застрявших в заливе, и предупреждали, что затор в Ормузе может рассасываться неделями даже после сделки.", "tone": "bullish", "tweet_ids": ["2066348854107087123", "2066368590928810057"]}, {"title_en": "SPR releases continue despite the deal", "title_ru": "Релизы SPR продолжаются несмотря на сделку", "blurb_en": "Even after the MoU, DoE kept feeding the market — about 8.89 mb last week, or roughly 1.3 mb/d — extending weeks of >1 mb/d SPR releases.", "blurb_ru": "Даже после MoU Минэнерго США продолжало кормить рынок: около 8,89 млн барр. за неделю, или примерно 1,3 млн б/с, продлевая недели релизов SPR выше 1 млн б/с.", "text_en": "Javier Blas stressed that despite the US-Iran deal, SPR releases would continue for a while, with last week's ~8.89 mb (~1.3 mb/d) helping keep the US market better supplied. That sat beside bullish SPR-stock headlines and framed government barrels as an ongoing overhang.", "text_ru": "Javier Blas подчеркивал, что несмотря на сделку США–Иран релизы SPR продлятся ещё какое-то время: около 8,89 млн барр. за прошлую неделю (~1,3 млн б/с) помогали лучше снабжать американский рынок. Это соседствовало с бычьими заголовками по запасам SPR и представляло госбаррели как продолжающийся навес.", "tone": "bearish", "tweet_ids": ["2066598768405827856"]}, {"title_en": "Faster Gulf restart vs fragile Lebanon clause", "title_ru": "Быстрый перезапуск Залива vs хрупкий пункт по Ливану", "blurb_en": "A pre-deal column still expected Persian Gulf production to restart faster than consensus, while Israel’s refusal to leave Lebanon underscored deal fragility.", "blurb_ru": "Колонка до сделки по-прежнему ждала более быстрого, чем консенсус, перезапуска добычи в Персидском заливе, а отказ Израиля уходить из Ливана подчёркивал хрупкость договорённостей.", "text_en": "Javier Blas reiterated his June 8 argument that Gulf oil restart would go much faster than many expect. Amena Bakr flagged Netanyahu telling Trump Israeli forces will not withdraw from Lebanon and do not feel bound by the MoU’s Lebanon clause — a direct hit to a core pillar of the deal.", "text_ru": "Javier Blas повторил тезис от 8 июня: перезапуск нефти в заливе пойдёт намного быстрее, чем ждут многие. Amena Bakr отметила слова Нетаньяху Трампу, что ЦАХАЛ не уйдёт из Ливана и Израиль не считает себя связанным ливанским пунктом MoU — прямой удар по опоре сделки.", "tone": "mixed", "tweet_ids": ["2066404221423911343", "2066347414135476367"]}]}}